comments: LaVine (CHI) wraps Poythress (ATL) and affects his FOM.
Dunn (CHI) cleanly steals the ball from Bazemore (ATL).
Len (ATL) makes contact with Dunn (CHI) and affects his SQBR.
Lopez (CHI) sets the screen on Huerter (ATL) and does not deliver contact.
Lopez (CHI) and Len (ATL) briefly engage and separate off ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Len (ATL) splits his feet before releasing his dribble.
Lopez (CHI) does not maintain verticality when he turns his body and brings his arms down in contact with Len's (ATL) body/arms, affecting his shot attempt.
Poythress (ATL) makes contact  Markkanen's (CHI) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Dunn (CHI) continues to move forward and makes contact to Huerter's (ATL) body during his shot attempt.
Lopez (CHI) sets the screen on Bazemore (ATL) and does not deliver contact.
LLS shows Bazemore (ATL) makes contact with LaVine's (CHI) arm and affects his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Lopez (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position during Len's (ATL) shot attempt.
Markkanen (CHI) cleanly deflects the loose ball away from Huerter (ATL).
[Observable in enhanced video] Huerter (ATL) is in the lane without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
RAR shows Adams (ATL) turns his shoulder and delivers contact to Harrison (CHI). The players tangle when disengaging and Harrison falls when he attempts to bring his leg around Adams.
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul on Huerter (ATL).
Lopez (CHI) sets the screen on Bembry (ATL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] LaVine (CHI) splits his feet before releasing his dribble.
Dunn (CHI) commits a take foul on Bazemore (ATL).
Bembry (ATL) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
Selden (CHI) commits a take foul on Len (ATL).
